{"tid":731754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日前度同我講左而句嘢","createTime":"2018-07-06T12:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T14:04:47.000Z","uid":95489,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"45221114dc50b4d860c852687735694327acb78e","tid":731754,"uid":95489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:42:35.000Z","msg":"我同咗佢一齊三年幾  上年分手唔夠一個月佢搵咗第二個<br />\n但我每日失眠好自責   覺得一直係我問題做得唔夠好<br />\n又成日去飲酒覺得好傷身。所以做咗好多嘢寄托一下 每日游水 踩車<br />\n佢知我忘記唔到佢 佢同男友嘈交會搵一搵我叫春之後又消失唔覆機又好返<br />\n但我發覺冇辦法唔諗起佢  等到而家佢突然搵我講對唔住 叫我唔好飲咁多會傷身<br />\n我於事打俾佢傾 問佢係關心我定係可憐我同內疚先咁講<br />\n佢不斷宛轉咁講 我叫佢直接啲講啦<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係咪我無論唔打擾你等你散咗之後 都冇可能同返你一齊 答係定唔係」<br />\n佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係 因為我已經入咗紙 驚你唔開心有抑鬱先唔講 」<br />\n<br />\n究竟我重要痛苦幾耐  人地要結婚我重可以做啲乜 好無助<br />\n明明我喺谷底爬緊上嚟又一次打沉我 想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f69d8067e2337f4685b9c469eb0edbbfb5baf9","tid":731754,"uid":144325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"請你好好放下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f011fdb21ccfa6274632f817230132f518d34b","tid":731754,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AFBobmCYNq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAFBobmCYNq0&d=G23sMlIDbip8kPqvS0Sf2P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=593966e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AFBobmCYNq0</a>"},{"pid":"8168e0092b70e469879d2960c1fda655a9780c45","tid":731754,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"嘩 一年就結婚<br />\n算啦 註定唔係你既另一半"},{"pid":"855bb3c4e680fa7ceac717e29f368c2da8e18a45","tid":731754,"uid":95489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"我係咪做咩都冇